snippet.title: Scavenging Changed this Duck's Life - ESCAPE FROM DUCKOV Game Trailer
snippet.description:
**ESCAPE FROM DUCKOV** is a single-player, top-down looter-shooter game. The game is set to launch on Steam in 2025.  

A demo test featuring approximately 6 hours of gameplay will be available on Steam starting at **8:00 PM PST on January 23** and will run for two weeks.  

Adding our game to your wishlist means a lot to us, and we'd love for you to join our community!  

👉 [Steam Store Page](https://store.steampowered.com/app/3167020/_/)  
👉 [Join our Discord](https://discord.gg/VTg4U87X)
